001package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.table.model;
002
003import lombok.AllArgsConstructor;
004import lombok.Getter;
005import org.openqa.selenium.By;
006
007/**
008 * Stores locator information for identifying key table elements in the UI.
009 *
010 * <p>This class is used to define locators for interacting with tables, including
011 * the table container, rows, and header row. It is primarily utilized in
012 * table-related operations within the test automation framework.
013 *
014 * <p>Used in table processing, row extraction, and validation operations.
015 *
016 * @author Cyborg Code Syndicate üíçüë®üíª
017 */
018@AllArgsConstructor
019@Getter
020public class TableLocators {
021
022   /**
023    * Locator for the table container element.
024    */
025   private By tableContainerLocator;
026
027   /**
028    * Locator for identifying all rows within the table.
029    */
030   private By tableRowsLocator;
031
032   /**
033    * Locator for the table's header row.
034    */
035   private By headerRowLocator;
036}
